Title: Coq Au Vin
Writer: Josh Thomas, Thomas Ward (additional writing), Liz Doran (additional writing), Hannah Gadsby (additional writing), Becky Lucas (additional writing)
Actors: Josh Thomas, Debra Lawrance, Emily Barclay, Hannah Gadsby
Plot: Claire brings her problems with her as she returns, Josh and Arnold discuss monogamy while Tom becomes more enamored with Ella. Hannah is irritated with Stuart and Josh comes to a grim decision about Adele the rooster's fate.
